name: International Conference on Exploring Colossal Technological Advances of the 21st Century in Science, Engineering, and Technology
content: The theme of the ICECTACSET conference is to provide unique results and challenges in the fields of science, engineering, technology, and management. This well-defined conference motto is to create crispy collaborations to draw together executives, researchers, scholars, and academics in all areas of Economics, business management, social sciences, and humanities together, to offer a globalized platform for the distribution of significant investigative results, distinguished approaches, and developmental applicability that focus on both modern methods and innovative approaches. Know more click www.icectaset.com
organizers: INSTITUTE FOR ENGINEERING RESEARCH AND PUBLICATION (IFERP)
